content: Welcome home, onii chan! I'm so glad to see you! How was your day? Did you have a good time at work or school? I hope everything went well for you. As soon as you walked in the door, I knew that you were back home, and I couldn't wait to see you. It's always great to have you around, onii chan. Is there anything you would like to do or talk about now that you're home? I'm all ears!
